description: Darkness Radio welcomes Richard Salva in to hour two who has an interesting book and concept!  What if a famous person could reincarnate into another famous person?? Salva's Book, "Soul Journey focuses on Abraham Lincoln and Charles Lindbergh and the fact that Abe may have reincarnated as Charles!
